```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as Next.js Frontend
    participant Backend as FastAPI Backend
    participant Prompt as PromptAgent
    participant Director as DirectorAgent
    participant Writer as WriterAgent
    participant Reviewer as ReviewerAgent
    participant Editor as EditorAgent
    participant Ollama as Ollama LLM
    participant ImageAgent as PersonalizedImageAgent
    participant WebUI as WebUI API Server
    participant DB as PostgreSQL Database
    participant FS as File System
    
    User->>Frontend: Enter story prompt + user photo (optional)
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/generate {prompt, use_personalized, user_photo}
    
    Backend->>Prompt: process_prompt(prompt)
    Prompt->>Prompt: Validate & classify
    Prompt-->>Backend: enhanced_prompt, prompt_type
    
    alt Invalid prompt
        Backend-->>Frontend: 400 Error: Invalid prompt
        Frontend-->>User: Show error message
    else Valid prompt
        
        rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Backend,Director: Story Text Generation Phase
        Backend->>Director: create_story(enhanced_prompt)
        
        Director->>Writer: generate_story(prompt)
        Writer->>Ollama: Generate story JSON
        Ollama-->>Writer: {title, setting, characters, scenes[]}
        Writer->>FS: Save draft JSON
        Writer-->>Director: story_draft
        
        Director->>Reviewer: review_story(story_draft)
        Reviewer->>Ollama: Validate & assess quality
        Ollama-->>Reviewer: review_feedback
        Reviewer->>FS: Save review JSON
        Reviewer-->>Director: reviewed_story
        
        Director->>Editor: edit_story(reviewed_story)
        Editor->>Editor: Polish & format
        Editor->>Editor: Generate PDF (ReportLab)
        Editor->>FS: Save PDF to exports/
        Editor->>FS: Save final story JSON
        Editor-->>Director: final_story + pdf_path
        
        Director-->>Backend: final_story
        end
        
        opt Image generation enabled
            rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
            Note over Backend,WebUI: Image Generation Phase (WebUI API)
            Note right of Backend: Pause Ollama to free GPU memory
            Backend->>Ollama: Pause service
            
            loop For each scene
                Backend->>ImageAgent: generate_image(scene, user_photo)
                
                ImageAgent->>WebUI: POST /sdapi/v1/txt2img {prompt, ip_adapter_image}
                Note right of WebUI: Load Realistic Vision model<br/>Inject IP-Adapter embedding<br/>First pass: txt2img (512x512)
                WebUI-->>ImageAgent: base_image
                
                ImageAgent->>WebUI: POST /sdapi/v1/img2img {image, denoise_strength}
                Note right of WebUI: Second pass: img2img refinement<br/>Upscale to 768x768
                WebUI-->>ImageAgent: final_image
                
                ImageAgent->>FS: Save PNG to images/
                ImageAgent-->>Backend: image_path
            end
            
            Note right of Backend: Resume Ollama after images complete
            Backend->>Ollama: Resume service
            end
        end
        
        rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Backend,DB: Database Save
        Backend->>DB: Save story metadata + user_id + mode + story_data
        DB-->>Backend: story_id
        end
        
        Backend-->>Frontend: {story, images[], pdf_path}
        Frontend->>Frontend: Render story UI
        Frontend-->>User: Display story with images and PDF link
    end
```
